arts.ttl: Nagelsmann shares thoughts on win over Netherlands: "It's deserved"

arts.ttl: Leweling modest after scoring debut winner for Germany: "Happy I could help"

arts.ttl: Baumann "happy, proud and thankful" after his Germany debut
arts.sum: TSG Hoffenheim goalkeeper Oliver Baumann has spoken about how much it meant to him to make his Germany debut against the Netherlands on Monday.

arts.ttl: Kimmich praises "outstanding" Leweling after win over Netherlands
arts.sum: Joshua Kimmich was full of praise for debutant Jamie Leweling after the Stuttgart man scored the winner in Germany's 1-0 win over the Netherlands on Monday.
